27</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">十一遊行要高叫「習近平下台」口號落中共面！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568634\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568634</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"87f55a5e53acd7651d73f85e8b74851cabd0ef6e","tid":1600091,"uid":174174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3a5d3fff2ed64e242420fc76dc02804e983aaf4c","tid":1600091,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:42:18.000Z","msg":"香港獨立"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:43:42.000Z","msg":"唯一出路！"},{"pid":"71b561a0915c3309bd7e5ccc711dba00932c3e4f","tid":1600091,"uid":304845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:46:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db6c7394e4e1edc2ff396f07e2e75f223d29aefc","tid":1600091,"uid":327169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:53:32.000Z","msg":"既然土共都講到出口，中英聯合聲明已經係過去咗嘅歷史，那有一國兩制，而家就一制，香港獨立!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab436354fb77ca2b61b0a10d164d22dc270f2333","tid":1600091,"uid":174174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db6c7394e4e1edc2ff396f07e2e75f223d29aefc","tid":1600091,"uid":327169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:53:32.000Z","msg":"既然土共都講到出口，中英聯合聲明已經係過去咗嘅歷史，那有一國兩制，而家就一制，香港獨立!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:57:32.000Z","msg":"共產黨統治都將會係過去咗嘅黑暗歷史"}]}